Package gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BedPanel
    A panel to display the bed status for a patient.
    BedsPanel
    The panel to layout out the status of each bed in the ward.
    CreateWardFrame
    The frame to obtain input to initialize the ward, and then it will start the main system.
    CreateWardPanel
    The panel to obtain input to initialize the ward, and then it will start the main system.
    SplitString
    A class to add "\n" into a string so as to break it up at a blank into lines of a specific length.
    ValueEntryPanel
    A panel with a prompt label and a text field for the entry of a data value.
    WardFrame
    The frame for the window to display the ward information, and allow the user to change the occupancy of beds.
    WardPanel
    The panel to display the ward information and allow the user to change the occupancy of beds.
